  <entry>
    <title>angr用法</title>
    <link href="http://yjw1029.github.io/ctf-tools/angr/Python%20angr%E7%94%A8%E6%B3%95.html"/>
    <id>http://yjw1029.github.io/ctf-tools/angr/Python angr用法.html</id>
    <published>2019-04-10T10:17:20.000Z</published>
    <updated>2019-04-10T12:31:24.647Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>angr的文档好像大多是英文的。我想要汇总为数不多的中文文档，并归纳英文教程和一些有用的api方便自己以后的查询和复习。如果有机会将建一个仓库存储中文angr文档。目前可以在categories -&gt; angr下阅读已归纳文档</p><a id="more"></a><h2 id="Install"><a href="#Install" class="headerlink" title="Install"></a>Install</h2><p>建议在虚拟环境下进行安装, virtulenv和pipenv皆可。</p><p>执行<code>pip install angr</code></p><h2 id="核心概念"><a href="#核心概念" class="headerlink" title="核心概念"></a>核心概念</h2><h3 id="顶级接口"><a href="#顶级接口" class="headerlink" title="顶级接口"></a>顶级接口</h3><p>首先你要引入一个二进制文件, 文档使用了<code>/bin/true</code>作为例子</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span><span class="keyword">import</span> angr</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span>proj = angr.Project(<span class="string">'/bin/true'</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="基本属性"><a href="#基本属性" class="headerlink" title="基本属性"></a>基本属性</h4><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span><span class="keyword">import</span> monkeyhex <span class="comment"># 这个会将数字结果转为16进制形式</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span>proj.arch </span><br><span class="line">&lt;Arch AMD64 (LE)&gt;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span>proj.entry</span><br><span class="line"><span class="number">0x401670</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span>proj.filename</span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">'/bin/true'</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>arch是archinfo.Arch对象的一个实例，用于编译程序的任何体系结构，在本例中为little-endian amd64。这个实例里包含很多的内容，正常情况下你可以使用<code>arch.bits</code>,<code>arch.bytes</code>获得你想要的信息。</p><h4 id="The-loader装载器"><a href="#The-loader装载器" class="headerlink" title="The loader装载器"></a>The loader装载器</h4><p> 他们使用了一个模块CLE，the loader就是CLE的结果。你可以通过访问<code>.loader</code>属性来使用它。现在你只用知道我们可以使用loader看到动态链接库和一些地址相关的问题, 我们之后会仔细的介绍它。</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span>proj.loader</span><br><span class="line">&lt;Loaded true, maps [<span class="number">0x400000</span>:<span class="number">0x5004000</span>]&gt;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span>proj.loader.share_objects <span class="comment"># 动态链接库</span></span><br><span class="line">&#123;<span class="string">'ld-linux-x86-64.so.2'</span>: &lt;ELF Object ld<span class="number">-2.24</span>.so, maps [<span class="number">0x2000000</span>:<span class="number">0x2227167</span>]&gt;,</span><br><span class="line"> <span class="string">'libc.so.6'</span>: &lt;ELF Object libc<span class="number">-2.24</span>.so, maps [<span class="number">0x1000000</span>:<span class="number">0x13c699f</span>]&gt;&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span>proj.loader.min_addr</span><br><span class="line"><span class="number">0x400000</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span>proj.loader.max_addr</span><br><span class="line"><span class="number">0x5004000</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span>proj.loader.main_object</span><br><span class="line">&lt;ELF Object true, maps [<span class="number">0x400000</span>:<span class="number">0x60721f</span>]&gt;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span>proj.loader.main_object.execstack <span class="comment"># 栈是否可执行</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="literal">False</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span>proj.loader.main_object.pic <span class="comment"># 是否开启了随机地址化</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="literal">True</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="The-factory-工厂"><a href="#The-factory-工厂" class="headerlink" title="The factory 工厂"></a>The factory 工厂</h4><h5 id="Blocks-块"><a href="#Blocks-块" class="headerlink" title="Blocks 块"></a>Blocks 块</h5><p><code>project.factory.block()</code>可以让你从一个给定的地址取出一个基本块(没有分支的代码)。angr以基本块作为它分析的基本单位。你可以得到一个Block对象，他可以告诉你很多关于这个基本块的有效信息。</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span>block = proj.factory.block(proj.entry) <span class="comment"># 从程序的入口点取出一个基本块</span></span><br><span class="line">&lt;Block <span class="keyword">for</span> <span class="number">0x401670</span>, <span class="number">42</span> bytes&gt;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span>block.pp()    <span class="comment"># 打印出反汇编结果</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="number">0x401670</span>:       xor     ebp, ebp</span><br><span class="line"><span class="number">0x401672</span>:       mov     r9, rdx</span><br><span class="line"><span class="number">0x401675</span>:       pop     rsi</span><br><span class="line"><span class="number">0x401676</span>:       mov     rdx, rsp</span><br><span class="line"><span class="number">0x401679</span>:       <span class="keyword">and</span>     rsp, <span class="number">0xfffffffffffffff0</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="number">0x40167d</span>:       push    rax</span><br><span class="line"><span class="number">0x40167e</span>:       push    rsp</span><br><span class="line"><span class="number">0x40167f</span>:       lea     r8, [rip + <span class="number">0x2e2a</span>]</span><br><span class="line"><span class="number">0x401686</span>:       lea     rcx, [rip + <span class="number">0x2db3</span>]</span><br><span class="line"><span class="number">0x40168d</span>:       lea     rdi, [rip - <span class="number">0xd4</span>]</span><br><span class="line"><span class="number">0x401694</span>:       call    qword ptr [rip + <span class="number">0x205866</span>]</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span>block.instructions    <span class="comment"># block中有多少条指令</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="number">0xb</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span>blcok.instruction_addrs    <span class="comment"># 打印出指令的地址</span></span><br><span class="line">[<span class="number">0x401670</span>, <span class="number">0x401672</span>, <span class="number">0x401675</span>, <span class="number">0x401676</span>, <span class="number">0x401679</span>, <span class="number">0x40167d</span>, <span class="number">0x40167e</span>, <span class="number">0x40167f</span>, <span class="number">0x401686</span>, <span class="number">0x40168d</span>, <span class="number">0x401694</span>]</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>另外你还可以使用Block对象得到其他基本块代码的表示</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span>blcok.capstone   <span class="comment"># capstone disassembly</span></span><br><span class="line">&lt;CapstoneBlock <span class="keyword">for</span> <span class="number">0x401670</span>&gt;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span>block.vex   <span class="comment"># VEX IRSB (that's a python internal address, not a program address)</span></span><br><span class="line">&lt;pyvex.block.IRSB at <span class="number">0x7706330</span>&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h5 id="States-状态"><a href="#States-状态" class="headerlink" title="States 状态"></a>States 状态</h5><p><code>Project</code>对象只表示程序的初始状态。如果你想使用angr了解程序执行状态，请使用一个特殊的对象——Simstate(一个伪程序状态)</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span>state = proj.factory.entry_state()</span><br><span class="line">&lt;SimState @ <span class="number">0x401670</span>&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>Simstate</p>]]></content>
    
    <summary type="html">
    
      &lt;p&gt;angr的文档好像大多是英文的。我想要汇总为数不多的中文文档，并归纳英文教程和一些有用的api方便自己以后的查询和复习。如果有机会将建一个仓库存储中文angr文档。目前可以在categories -&amp;gt; angr下阅读已归纳文档&lt;/p&gt;
    
