  <entry>
    <title>Python z3用法</title>
    <link href="http://yjw1029.github.io/ctf-tools/Python%20z3%E7%94%A8%E6%B3%95.html"/>
    <id>http://yjw1029.github.io/ctf-tools/Python z3用法.html</id>
    <published>2019-04-08T12:20:00.000Z</published>
    <updated>2019-04-10T10:19:47.105Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>最近在做pico和打比赛的时候听说了z3强大的计算功能，在这里记录一下。z3可以解决多项式问题，对固定长度bit流也可以做位运算处理。</p><a id="more"></a><h2 id="Install-安装方法"><a href="#Install-安装方法" class="headerlink" title="Install 安装方法"></a>Install 安装方法</h2><p>直接下载<a href="https://github.com/angr" target="_blank" rel="noopener">angr</a>,一个非常好用的符号分析工具之后也会用到</p><h2 id="入门学习"><a href="#入门学习" class="headerlink" title="入门学习"></a>入门学习</h2><h3 id="基本操作"><a href="#基本操作" class="headerlink" title="基本操作"></a>基本操作</h3><ol><li><p>定义整形变量：<code>x = Int(&#39;x&#39;)</code>, <code>y = Int(&#39;y&#39;)</code></p></li><li><p>解不等式：<code>solve(约束条件1，约束条件2，··· 约束条件n)</code> 使用运算符&lt;, &lt;=, &gt;, &gt;=, ==, != 来进行比较</p></li><li><p>使用simplify()进行表达式化简:</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">x = Int(<span class="string">'x'</span>)</span><br><span class="line">y = Int(<span class="string">'y'</span>)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">print</span> simplify(x + y + <span class="number">2</span>*x +<span class="number">3</span>)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">print</span> simplify(x &lt; y + x + <span class="number">2</span>)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">print</span> simplify(And(x+<span class="number">1</span>&gt;=<span class="number">3</span>, x**<span class="number">2</span> + x**<span class="number">2</span> + y**<span class="number">2</span> + <span class="number">2</span> &gt;= <span class="number">5</span>))</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>输出：</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="number">3</span> + <span class="number">3</span>*x + y</span><br><span class="line">Not(y &lt;= <span class="number">-2</span>)</span><br><span class="line">And(x &gt;= <span class="number">2</span>, <span class="number">2</span>*x**<span class="number">2</span> + y**<span class="number">2</span> &gt;= <span class="number">3</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p><code>set_option(html_mode = True)</code>使得Z3Py以Z3Py表示法显示</p></li><li><p>Z3 提供遍历表达式的函数</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">x = Int(<span class="string">'x'</span>)</span><br><span class="line">y = Int(<span class="string">'y'</span>)</span><br><span class="line">n = x + y &gt;= <span class="number">3</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">print</span> <span class="string">"num args: "</span>, n.num_args()</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">print</span> <span class="string">"children: "</span>, n.children()</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">print</span> <span class="string">"1st child: "</span>, n.arg(<span class="number">0</span>)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">print</span> <span class="string">"2nd child: "</span>, n.arg(<span class="number">1</span>)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">print</span> <span class="string">"operator: "</span>, n.decl()</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">print</span> <span class="string">"op name: "</span>, n.decl().name()</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>输出：</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">num args: <span class="number">2</span></span><br><span class="line">children: [x+y, <span class="number">3</span>]</span><br><span class="line"><span class="number">1</span>st child: x+y</span><br><span class="line"><span class="number">2</span>nd child: <span class="number">3</span></span><br><span class="line">operator: &gt;=</span><br><span class="line">op name: &gt;=</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p><code>Real(&#39;x&#39;) Reals(&#39;x y z&#39;)</code>创建实数变量。z3py可以表示任意大的整数，有理数和无理数。使用<code>set_option(preciosion=num)</code>可以将结果显示精确到指定的位数。输出时<code>?</code>表示输出被截断。</p><p>注： set_option()用于配置z3全局环境</p></li><li><p>注意z3py中 <code>1/3</code>是python表达式而不是有理数</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 有理数的正确表示方法 1/3</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">print</span> Q(<span class="number">1</span>,<span class="number">3</span>)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">print</span> RealVal(<span class="number">1</span>)/<span class="number">3</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">x = Int(<span class="string">'x'</span>)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">print</span> x + Q(<span class="number">1</span>,<span class="number">3</span>)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">print</span> x + <span class="string">"1/3"</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">print</span> x + <span class="number">0.25</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p><code>set_option(rational_to_decimal=True)</code>可以强制将有理数输出为十进制小数</p></li><li><p>若约束条件不可满足，系统会输出<code>no solution</code></p></li></ol><h3 id="布尔逻辑"><a href="#布尔逻辑" class="headerlink" title="布尔逻辑"></a>布尔逻辑</h3><p>Z3支持Bool运算符： And, Or, Not, Implies(implication), If(if-then-else)和==运算符</p><ol><li>定义布尔变量 <code>Bool(&#39;p&#39;)</code> `x, y ,z = Bools(‘x y z’)</li><li>Implies(p, q)表示p蕴含q</li><li>使用solve添加布尔运算约束条件，当三个布尔表达式皆为真时求得解。</li><li>基本布尔运算符And()与, Or()或，Not()非，Nand()与非，Nor()或非，Xor()异或，Implies()蕴含，Equivalent()双蕴含，If(t1, t2, t3)若t1为真t2否则为t3</li><li>True Flase 作为bool常量</li></ol><h3 id="求解器"><a href="#求解器" class="headerlink" title="求解器"></a>求解器</h3><ol><li><p>基本用法</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">x = Int(<span class="string">'x'</span>)</span><br><span class="line">y = Int(<span class="string">'y'</span>)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 定义求解器</span></span><br><span class="line">s = Solver() <span class="comment">#求解器初始时为空</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 添加约束条件</span></span><br><span class="line">s.add(x&gt;<span class="number">10</span>, y==x+<span class="number">2</span>) </span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 判断是否有解，有解返回sat 无解返回unsat</span></span><br><span class="line">s.check()</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 保存当前的约束条件至一个栈中</span></span><br><span class="line">s.push()</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 从栈中取出最近一次保存的约束条件作为当前的约束条件</span></span><br><span class="line">s.pop()</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>z3可以解决线性多项式，非线性多项式的问题z3将无法解决返回unknown</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">x = Real(<span class="string">'x'</span>)</span><br><span class="line">s = Solver()</span><br><span class="line">s.add(<span class="number">2</span>**x == <span class="number">3</span>)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">print</span> s.check()</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>输出</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">unknown</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>遍历/性能统计</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">x,y = Reals(<span class="string">'x y'</span>)</span><br><span class="line">s = Solver()</span><br><span class="line">s.add(x&gt;<span class="number">1</span>, y&gt;<span class="number">1</span>, Or(x+y&gt;<span class="number">3</span>, x-y&lt;<span class="number">2</span>))</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 打印约束条件</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">for</span> c <span class="keyword">in</span> s.assertations():</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">print</span> c</span><br><span class="line">    </span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 检查是否有满足约束条件的解</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">print</span> s.check()</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 性能统计</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">print</span> s.statistics()</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">for</span> k,v <span class="keyword">in</span> s.statistics():</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">print</span> <span class="string">"%s, %s"</span> % (k,v)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>检查模型，用于输出Solver()的解</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 输入约束条件</span></span><br><span class="line">x, y, z = Reals(<span class="string">'x y z'</span>)</span><br><span class="line">s = Solver()</span><br><span class="line">s.add(x&gt;<span class="number">1</span>, y&gt;<span class="number">1</span>, x+y&gt;<span class="number">3.</span> z-x&lt;<span class="number">10</span>)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">print</span> s.check()</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 开始使用模型求解了，只会输出第一个解</span></span><br><span class="line">m = s.model()</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 输出x变量的解</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">print</span> <span class="string">"x =%s"</span> % m[x]</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 输出所有的解</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">for</span> d <span class="keyword">in</span> m.decls():</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">print</span> <span class="string">'%s = %s'</span> % (d.name(), m[d])</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ol><h3 id="ARITHMETIC-算数"><a href="#ARITHMETIC-算数" class="headerlink" title="ARITHMETIC 算数"></a>ARITHMETIC 算数</h3><p>z3支持实数Real和整数变量Int, 同时z3也支持强制类型转换</p><ol><li><p>整数/实数变量</p><p><code>ToReal()</code>将整形表达式转换为实型表达式</p></li><li><p>在solve()中可以混合使用Int和Real</p></li><li><p>Simplify 可添加简化类型</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">x, y = Reals(<span class="string">'x y'</span>)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 单项式相加形式的化简</span></span><br><span class="line">t = simplify((x+y)**<span class="number">3</span>, som=<span class="literal">True</span>)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">print</span> t</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 将乘合并为幂</span></span><br><span class="line">t = simplify(t, mul_to_power=<span class="literal">True</span>)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">print</span> t</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>输出：</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">x*x*x + <span class="number">3</span>*x*x*y + <span class="number">3</span>*x*y*y + y*y*y</span><br><span class="line">x**<span class="number">3</span> + <span class="number">3</span>*x**<span class="number">2</span>*y + <span class="number">3</span>*x*y**<span class="number">2</span> + y**<span class="number">3</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>z3内允许两种书写风格, <code>help_simplify()</code>可以打印所有可用选项</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">x,y = Reals(<span class="string">'x y'</span>)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 第一种风格</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">print</span> simplify(x == y+<span class="number">2</span>, <span class="string">':arith-lhs'</span>, <span class="literal">True</span>)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 第二种风格</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">print</span> simplify(x == y+<span class="number">2</span>, arith_lhs=<span class="literal">True</span>)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">help_simplify()</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>无理数、任意大</p><p>z3py可以显示较大的整数，有理数和无理数执行基本算数。z3py始终以10进制形式显示无理数，但是也可以使用<code>sexpr()</code>方法提取。它以Lisp-like的形式显示数学公式和表达式的z3内部表示。<code>sexpr()</code>对所有的z3表达式都有效</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">x,y = Reals(<span class="string">'x y'</span>)</span><br><span class="line">solve(x + <span class="number">10000000000000000000000</span> == y, y &gt; <span class="number">20000000000000000</span>)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">print</span> Sqrt(<span class="number">2</span>) + Sqrt(<span class="number">3</span>)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">print</span> simplify(Sqrt(<span class="number">2</span>) + Sqrt(<span class="number">3</span>))</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">print</span> simplify(Sqrt(<span class="number">2</span>) + Sqrt(<span class="number">3</span>)).sexpr()</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">print</span> (x + Sqrt(y) * <span class="number">2</span>).sexpr()</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>输出：</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">[y = <span class="number">20000000000000001</span>, x = <span class="number">-9999979999999999999999</span>]</span><br><span class="line"><span class="number">2</span>**(<span class="number">1</span>/<span class="number">2</span>) + <span class="number">3</span>**(<span class="number">1</span>/<span class="number">2</span>)</span><br><span class="line">3.1462643699?</span><br><span class="line">(root-obj (+ (^ x <span class="number">4</span>) (* (- <span class="number">10</span>) (^ x <span class="number">2</span>)) <span class="number">1</span>) <span class="number">4</span>)</span><br><span class="line">(+ x (* (^ y (/ <span class="number">1.0</span> <span class="number">2.0</span>)) <span class="number">2.0</span>))</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ol><h3 id="MACHINE-ARITHMETIC-机器算数"><a href="#MACHINE-ARITHMETIC-机器算数" class="headerlink" title="MACHINE ARITHMETIC 机器算数"></a>MACHINE ARITHMETIC 机器算数</h3><p>现代CPU和主流编程语言使用<strong>固定大小</strong>的位向量进行算术运算。 机器算术在Z3Py中可用作<strong>位向量</strong>。 它们实现<strong>无符号</strong>和<strong>有符号二补数</strong>算术的精确语义。</p><p><strong> 位向量: </strong></p><p><code>BitVec(&#39;x&#39;,16)</code>用于创建一个16位的x位向量变量。BitVecVal(10, 32)用于创建一个32位值为10的位向量常量</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">x = BitVec(<span class="string">'x'</span>, <span class="number">16</span>)</span><br><span class="line">y = BitVec(<span class="string">'y'</span>, <span class="number">16</span>)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">print</span> x + <span class="number">2</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">print</span> (x + <span class="number">2</span>).sexpr()</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">print</span> simplify(x + y - <span class="number">1</span>)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">a = BitVecVal(<span class="number">-1</span>, <span class="number">16</span>)</span><br><span class="line">b = BitVelVal(<span class="number">-1</span>, <span class="number">16</span>)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">print</span> simplify(a == b)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">a = BitVecVal(<span class="number">-1</span>, <span class="number">32</span>)</span><br><span class="line">b = BitVecVal(<span class="number">65535</span>, <span class="number">32</span>)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">print</span> simplify(a == b)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>输出：</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">x + <span class="number">2</span></span><br><span class="line">(bvadd x <span class="comment">#x0002)</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="number">65535</span> + x + y</span><br><span class="line"><span class="literal">True</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="literal">False</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>Z3中区分有无符号数运算。z3py中运算符<code>&lt;</code>,<code>&lt;=</code>,<code>&gt;</code>,<code>&gt;=</code>,<code>/</code>,<code>%</code>,<code>&gt;&gt;</code> 对应于有符号版本。<code>ULT</code>,<code>ULE</code>,<code>UGT</code>,<code>ULE</code>,<code>UDiv</code>,<code>URem</code>,<code>LShR</code>。</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">x,y = BitVecs(<span class="string">'x y'</span>, <span class="number">32</span>)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">solve(x + y == <span class="number">2</span> ,x &gt; <span class="number">0</span>, y &gt; <span class="number">0</span>)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">solve(x &amp; y == ~y)</span><br><span class="line">solve(x &lt; <span class="number">0</span>)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 无符号版本 &lt;</span></span><br><span class="line">solve(ULT(X, <span class="number">0</span>))</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>输出</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">[y = <span class="number">1</span>, x = <span class="number">1</span>]</span><br><span class="line">[y = <span class="number">4294967295</span>, x = <span class="number">0</span>]</span><br><span class="line">[x = <span class="number">4294967295</span>]</span><br><span class="line">no solution</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong> 位移运算: </strong> <code>&lt;&lt;</code> <code>&gt;&gt;</code></p><h3 id="FUCTIONS-函数"><a href="#FUCTIONS-函数" class="headerlink" title="FUCTIONS 函数"></a>FUCTIONS 函数</h3><p><code>Function</code>函数: 可以用来解符合要求的的函数</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">x = Int(<span class="string">'x'</span>)</span><br><span class="line">y = Int(<span class="string">'y'</span>)</span><br><span class="line">f = Function(<span class="string">'f'</span>, Insort(), Insort())</span><br><span class="line">solve(f(f(x)) == x, f(x) == y, x != y)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>输出</p><figure class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">[x = 0, y = 1, f = [0 -&gt; 1, 1 -&gt; 0, else -&gt; 1]]</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>我们也可以评估模型中的约束系统表达式</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">x = Int(<span class="string">'x'</span>)</span><br><span class="line">y = Int(<span class="string">'y'</span>)</span><br><span class="line">f = Function(<span class="string">'f'</span>, IntSort(), IntSort())</span><br><span class="line">s = Solver()</span><br><span class="line">s.add(f(f(x)) == x, f(x) == y, x != y)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">print</span> s.check()</span><br><span class="line">m = s.model()</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">print</span> <span class="string">"f(f(x)) ="</span>, m.evaluate(f(f(x)))</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">print</span> <span class="string">"f(x) ="</span>, m.evaluation(f(x))</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>输出：</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sat</span><br><span class="line">f(f(x)) = 0</span><br><span class="line">f(x) = 1</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
    <summary type="html">
    
      &lt;p&gt;最近在做pico和打比赛的时候听说了z3强大的计算功能，在这里记录一下。z3可以解决多项式问题，对固定长度bit流也可以做位运算处理。&lt;/p&gt;
    
    </summary>
    
